exthheader.author: Ted Pattison
exthheader.description: Take advantage of the most important new concept in Microsoft® SharePoint® 2013--the app. Led by two SharePoint experts, you’ll learn development techniques such as building app lists, creating event handlers, and the major classes in the object model that provide access to content stored in SharePoint.
exthheader.subject: COMPUTERS / Enterprise Applications / Collaboration Software
